subject: Baseball
Prices (Fares, Fees and Rates)
Yankee Stadium (NYC)
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: After raising ticket prices for nonpremium seats by 86 percent this season, the Yankees will soon announce prices for their playoff tickets, and fans could end up paying steep premiums.
